						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up on the tank bund.</p>						

						<p>This undated record may be assigned to the 18th century on the basis of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>It states the construction of a tank by Rājā Kāmerāju Bahdūr on the orders of <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Kaṭhāri Sāḷva Bommarāju Bahadūr.</p>						

